  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd6 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Here are the postage rates",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "By raising local postal charges, the average postal charge which was 15 rupees has been increased by 233 percent to 50 rupees.",
        "Steps have been taken to raise the registered postage fee which was 30 rupees to 60 rupees, and the postage fee of charities and voluntary organizations which was 12 rupees to 30 rupees.",
        "Along with this rate hike, steps have been taken to increase all local postal rates."
      ],
